                  ("glVertexAttrib4N~v" index ~X))
           ((s16 4) (s8 4) (u8 4) (u16 4) (s32 4) (u32 4))
           "bad argument for gl-vertex-attrib-4n: %S"
           ;; We can't use 'args' as a fallback, for we need to coerce
